Well, when bow kiting crap in T2, I occassionally get an add and have to root one or the other.  When I root my original target mob (or snare it and run out of range) it almost immediately regens to full.  Like within 2 ticks.<br>
<br>
If you want to test it, go snare something and nuke it down a bit.  Then run out of chase range, and right back in. <p><font face="tahoma" size=-1><b><a href="http://moresoda.com/eq/">Labiara Stankfoot</a><br>
