<br>
Also, I believe I have noticed that charmed pet's damage is not assigned to the master.  Therefore any damage done by the pet does not count toward that groups damage.  Hypothetically, I think that if in your situation, the druid did 9% damage, the charmed pet did 81% damage, and you did 10%, then you would get the kill (though I have not done testing on this).<br>
<br>
Aven, the newbie wizard.<br>
